message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your needs and endeavors. Considering its value and the benefits it provides, I propose a price of $14,000 for this exceptional item. This offer is designed to be mutually beneficial, providing you with a high-quality solution at a price that reflects its worth while ensuring a fair return for us. Please let me know if you have any questions or if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
